# 💰 Finance Investment Dashboard

> 📊 An interactive Excel Dashboard built using Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, Slicers, and Data Visualization techniques to analyze investment behavior, financial goals, and spending patterns.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project analyzes a **Finance Investment Dataset** to understand how individuals invest, save, and manage their finances. The dashboard provides insights into investment avenues, financial objectives, savings goals, expenditure, and demographic distribution.

The dashboard was created in **Microsoft Excel** using:
- 📊 Pivot Tables
- 📈 Pivot Charts
- 🎯 Slicers
- 🎨 Dashboard Formatting
- 📋 Data Cleaning

